  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/digitalcamera/\" rel=\"tag\">数码相机</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/29/ricoh-gr-limited-edition/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/b6011581943ce130b5eb6c5a9d1b88a9/13_tn.jpg\" /></a></p>\n圣诞节快到，Ricoh 也趁机推出全球 5,000 部军绿色 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/gr\">GR</a> 限量版，为简约的外型添几份独特。这部限量版同样搭配 1,620 万像素的 APS-C CMOS 感光组件及等效焦距 28mm 最大光圈 f/2.8 镜头，在设计上选用带有光泽的军绿色波浪暗纹机身，手抦从仿皮改成带有木质效果的大理石纹设计手柄，整体质感提升了不少。配件方面，遮光罩及转接器均用上银色镀膜，与机身互相映照，还有复古味道的棕色相机肩带及相机袋。整个套装要价 HK$7,490（约 5,900 元人民币），机身的其他细节可在图集内观看啊！<br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/ricoh-gr-limited-edition/\">Ricoh GR Limited Edition</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/ricoh-gr-limited-edition/6361407/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/11/03tn-1385739083_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/ricoh-gr-limited-edition/6361408/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/11/07tn-1385739086_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/ricoh-gr-limited-edition/6361409/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/11/08tn-1385739089_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/ricoh-gr-limited-edition/6361410/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/11/12tn_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/ricoh-gr-limited-edition/6361411/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/11/13tn_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/29/ricoh-gr-limited-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"P